description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Power Yoga Flow' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Rhythmic Powerhouse and The Groove Session vibe.
The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly. The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Move with Owen in this faster paced power flow accessible to all levels. *Yoga blocks recommended.  ...
